data.title: fu-wah
data.text:
Welcome to Fu-Wah, your neighborhood mini market and deli. Since opening our doors for the first time in 1982, Fu-Wah has remained a family-run University City staple. For over 30 years, we have been proud to watch our community grow around us. While the surroundings may change, our commitment to serving quality products has not. Home to the Original Tofu Banh Mi, Fu-Wah provides freshly made deli items such as bold Banh Mi styles and classic hoagies and sandwiches.
